{
  "stem": "13911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You didn't eat, you didn't drink, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a blessing in disguise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was so embarrassing, you-- you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was no food, of course?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The raw potato-- funny how you survive without food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't need any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, food-- you didn't think of food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Honestly!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not human beings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, we just-- you're surviving, surviving, like-- hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- you didn't-- the end result, you didn't care what if you survive or how-- how on earth can you think of surviving, where there is no escape?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We know that it has-- why-- why kill the others?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why kill my mother and my father, my sisters, and anybody else, and not me?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What am I, chosen to-- So we knew there was no-- I don't know what we were thinking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just-- just looking-- Was there any conversation?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If there was, it was-- first of all, you had no strength to talk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you tried, to, let's say, to stand up, to attend to your human needs, the dress was hanging.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I wish I can lose, uh-- [LAUGH] something, now, that there I lost like-- didn't need to go on a diet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On a special diet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody became a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, when you walked, you had to hold on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no energy, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you mentioned, after 15 days, it seemed safe to come out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we saw already people-- ants crawling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we come out and realize that the pogrom is over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, they are preparing a smaller-- Actually, it was where the dead ghetto they put us-- in dead ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Living ghetto, no more-- finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now it's only the dead ghetto they put us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
